02:19.320 --> 02:21.720
They're children!
How could you do that?

02:21.800 --> 02:25.440
Oh, sure. First you dump all over it,
now you wanna know how it's done.

02:25.560 --> 02:28.080
- And I wanted to apologize.
- Well, he hasn't been here.

02:28.160 --> 02:31.920
But he said he was
staying here. Oh, my God.

02:32.000 --> 02:34.640
- Maybe he's staying with another woman.
- No, no, no. No, no.

02:34.720 --> 02:37.920
He is staying here.
I just haven't seen him here...

02:38.000 --> 02:40.080
the foyer or the kitchen.

02:40.160 --> 02:43.680
- Well, that's a relief.
- Yeah.

02:43.800 --> 02:47.320
- Well, tell him to call me when he gets in.
- I sure will, Marta.

02:47.400 --> 02:49.360
- If you remember.
- I will remember.

02:49.440 --> 02:52.160
Yeah. I'll give him
the message though. Okay.

02:52.240 --> 02:54.520
- She's gone.
- Yep. Got it.

02:54.600 --> 02:56.960
- You are too nice.
- Oh, come on. What was I supposed to do?

02:57.080 --> 03:00.400
Tell her that Gob is not staying here?
Tell her Gob is screwing around on her?

03:00.480 --> 03:03.840
God knows where he is?
Actually, that-that sounded okay.

03:03.960 --> 03:05.880
Nah, you'll never be able to do it.
You're too good.

03:06.000 --> 03:08.000
- You're the noble one.
- Thank you.

03:08.120 --> 03:09.920
- The one who never wins.
- I-I don't know about that.

03:10.040 --> 03:12.360
- The loser. The fool.
- Hmm?

03:14.560 --> 03:17.280
She is such a hypocrite.
Doesn't it drive you nuts?

03:17.400 --> 03:20.280
- Crazy. Wait. Who is? Which part?
- My mom.

03:20.360 --> 03:22.720
She pretends to care
about all these causes.

03:22.840 --> 03:25.040
<i>Lindsay had always been celebrated...</i>

03:25.120 --> 03:28.920
<i>for her wine and cheese
charity fund-raisers.</i>

03:31.840 --> 03:33.498
I mean, now she's anti-leather?

03:33.499 --> 03:36.600
Let's see how she feels when
her daughter's pro-leather.

03:36.680 --> 03:39.840
Wanna go shopping with me?
I bet you could get something cool.

03:39.960 --> 03:43.120
<i>In fact, George Michael
had been trying to prove to Maeby...</i>

03:43.200 --> 03:46.200
<i>that he was macho, after
an embarrassing brush with her.</i>

03:46.320 --> 03:49.440
Your legs look exactly like mine,
and I just shaved mine.

03:51.080 --> 03:52.880
So I'm thinking of getting a motorcycle.

03:52.960 --> 03:55.112
I'm gonna need a leather
jacket when I'm on my hog

03:55.113 --> 03:56.800
and need to go into a controlled slide.

03:56.920 --> 04:02.160
There's my little girl. I've got great news.
Daddy has the entire day off.

04:02.240 --> 04:04.520
But you have every day off.
You don't have a job.

04:04.640 --> 04:08.200
Well... I don't need money to hang
out with my daughter. Where are you going?

04:08.320 --> 04:10.720
- We're going shopping.
- Oh, no, no. I can't do that.

04:10.840 --> 04:14.160
<i>The next day, Michael
was stopped on his way to work.</i>

04:14.240 --> 04:15.960
<i>- Get in.
- What?</i>

04:16.040 --> 04:19.480
If you care about your brother,
you'll get in this car.

04:19.560 --> 04:23.080
- Which brother?
- Gob.

